From: galaunay <gaby.launay@tutanota.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Apr 2018 19:51:53 +0100
Subject: Update failing tests in Travis (#1342)

* Use a rpc timeout of 100 for all test

Avoid failing tests due to rpc timeout, that can happen
for slow computers and Travis.

* Fix xref-reference test, failing in Travis.
---
 test/elpy-xref--references-test.el | 25 +++++++++++++------------
 test/test-helper.el                |  1 +
 2 files changed, 14 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

